@beyonce has announced via Instagram the relaunch of @weareivypark in collaboration with @adidas, having left her original retail partner @topshop in 2018. @beyonce now owns the company and her collab will launch January 18th 2020. #ivypark #beyonce 📸 Regram @beyonce

Take it to the subway 🚇 @itsjeremyscott for @moschino staged his Pre-Fall 2020 runway show in the @nytransitmuseum and the collection was an homage to New York - gigantic caps, enlarged backpacks, hoodies and oversized jewellery. “New York is the city that never sleeps,” said Scott. “With that in mind, I wanted to offer a little bit of everything...” #prefall #moschino 📸 Regram @moschino

Congratulations to Rihanna, whose  label Fenty won the Urban Luxe award at last night’s Fashion Awards. Other winners included the in-demand Daniel Lee for Bottega Veneta, who won four awards including Designer of the Year; Sarah Burton of Alexander McQueen who won the Trailblazer Award and Adut Akech who was Model of the Year. @badgalriri @bottegaveneta @alexandermcqueen @adutakech #britishfashionawards #fenty
